d to dule you should of duled him as a whole and then stepped back and look at the results.<br>
<br>
When I was level 49 me and my pet could go in the grimling mines over in TM and clear the mines and have time to med before the respawns would start (not that much med time was needed since the pet can kill most on his own and regen up in no time).  I also have a level 48 warrior and my brother has a 46 cleric.  We went there as a team and fought in the same cave.  We could not finish half of the spawns in the mines before they would start respawning.  From my mage point of veiw I think &quot;Kewl&quot; I am kicking tail and taking names.  From my warriors point of view this is jut not right at all.  For a blue pet to be able to wipe the floor like that with me is just no where fair.  That said the least they should do is allow the melee to beat that pet if he had to dule him.<br>
<br>
ROFL - Just my two cents on the subject - no offense intended at all.  <br>
